# Copy this file to `.secret.local` (same folder) and paste your real key.
# `.secret.local` is gitignored — never commit your real key.
#
# The Firebase Functions emulator reads secret values (defineSecret) from this
# file for LOCAL testing. In production the key is stored in Cloud Secret
# Manager instead, via:
#   firebase functions:secrets:set OPENAI_API_KEY
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key-here
